Permitted Purpose

A permitted purpose is any noncommercial purpose.

Personal uses are for a noncommercial purpose. Personal uses include research, experimentation, testing for public knowledge, personal study, private entertainment, hobby projects, amateur pursuits, or religious observance, as long as you do not anticipate any commercial application.

Use by any of the following is for a noncommercial purpose, regardless of their funding sources or obligations:

